Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.39,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,¿¡Q-Qué?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:58.96,Dragon Ball,,0,0,0,,No la hemos cambiado desde la primavera pasada...
